---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import TextTransformer from '@/components/TextTransformer';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="TikTok Font Generator" 
  description="Create trendy TikTok-style fonts perfect for social media, bios, and viral content"
>
  <TextTransformer 
    client:load
    title="TikTok Font Generator" 
    description="Generate trendy fonts that are perfect for TikTok" 
    transformType="tiktok"
    placeholder="Enter your text to create TikTok-style fonts..."
  />

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 shadow rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">About TikTok Font Generator</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <p>The TikTok Font Generator creates trendy, modern fonts that are perfect for TikTok content, social media posts, and any platform where you want to capture that viral, Gen-Z aesthetic that makes content stand out.</p>
          <p>TikTok's visual culture emphasizes clean, modern typography that's both readable and stylish, perfect for short-form content that needs to grab attention quickly.</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">TikTok Font Features</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Sans-Serif Style:</strong> Clean, modern letterforms without decorative strokes</li>
            <li><strong>High Readability:</strong> Optimized for mobile viewing and quick reading</li>
            <li><strong>Trendy Aesthetic:</strong> Matches current social media design trends</li>
            <li><strong>Unicode Compatible:</strong> Works across all social media platforms</li>
            <li><strong>Mobile Optimized:</strong> Displays perfectly on smartphones and tablets</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">Perfect for TikTok</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Bio Text:</strong> Make your TikTok bio stand out from the crowd</li>
            <li><strong>Video Captions:</strong> Add stylish text overlays to your videos</li>
            <li><strong>Comments:</strong> Make your comments more noticeable</li>
            <li><strong>Usernames:</strong> Create memorable, stylish usernames</li>
            <li><strong>Hashtags:</strong> Make your hashtags more visually appealing</li>
            <li><strong>Story Text:</strong> Enhance your story posts with trendy fonts</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">TikTok Content Strategy</h3>
          <p>Using stylish fonts can help with:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Increased Engagement:</strong> Eye-catching text gets more attention</li>
            <li><strong>Brand Recognition:</strong> Consistent font use builds your personal brand</li>
            <li><strong>Algorithm Boost:</strong> Unique content may get better reach</li>
            <li><strong>Professional Look:</strong> Polished text makes content look more professional</li>
            <li><strong>Trend Participation:</strong> Stay current with visual trends</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">Cross-Platform Use</h3>
          <p>This font also works great on:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Instagram posts, stories, and reels</li>
            <li>Twitter/X posts and bio</li>
            <li>YouTube video titles and descriptions</li>
            <li>Snapchat stories and messages</li>
            <li>Discord servers and messages</li>
            <li>WhatsApp status and messages</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">TikTok Typography Trends</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Clean, minimalist fonts for maximum readability</li>
            <li>Sans-serif styles that work well on mobile screens</li>
            <li>Fonts that complement video content without distraction</li>
            <li>Typography that appeals to younger demographics</li>
            <li>Styles that work well with TikTok's interface design</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">Best Practices</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Keep text concise for better impact</li>
            <li>Test fonts on mobile devices first</li>
            <li>Ensure good contrast with background colors</li>
            <li>Use consistently across your content</li>
            <li>Consider your target audience and niche</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">Create content that's ready to go viral with TikTok-perfect typography! ðŸ“±âœ¨</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
